From the authors: Due to poor resolution it is not
possible to say exactly what inelastic scattering
occurs in the region 2.0 MeV to 2.5 MeV scattered
neutron energy, and therefore the elastic scattering
cross section quoted below may include a contribution
from inelastic scattering with small energy loss.

added to REACTION code. E-MIN was added.
